quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Then Pharaoh sent his marshals to the cities
  26,54,"[saying], \"[The Children of Israel] are a small band"
  26,55,but they are offending us
  26,56,and we are a vigilant society
  26,57,"So We expelled them from [their] gardens and springs"
  26,58,treasures and honored estates
  26,59,"Thus it was. [In time], We caused the Children of Israel to inherit all of this"
  26,60,"So, they [the Egyptians] pursued them at sunrise"
  26,61,"and when the two sides sighted one another, Moses' companions' said, \"We will be overtaken"
  26,62,"[Moses] said, \"No! my Lord is with me; He will guide me"
  26,63,"Then, We revealed to Moses, \"Strike with your staff the sea.\" It parted, and each part looked like a mountain"
  26,64,We brought the pursuers right into it
  26,65,and We saved Moses and all who were with him
  26,66,and We drowned the others
  26,67,"There is a sign in this, but most of them will not believe"
  26,68,"Truly your Lord is the Almighty, the Merciful-to-all"
  26,69,Tell them the story of Abraham